To address the issues of overlapping and blocking elements effectively, I will completely remove the circular "physical table" metaphor on desktop.

Instead, I will implement a **Unified Dashboard Layout** for all screen sizes. This approach separates the "Stage" (Story Info & Results) from the "Team" (User Cards), ensuring that:
1.  **No Blocking:** The Story/Results panel is at the top/center, and user cards are arranged in a responsive grid below it.
